so the past few weeks have been kinda weirdly sucking and i don't know why. but this weekend was better

friday, me jen and pema made the best cupcakes like ever. they were the shit. literally. prettttty cool. and it snowed like a beast, not fun.

saturday, i shoveled with jamjam in the wee morning hours. and we made fiddy bucks. not too shabby. and thennn steph nitopi's sweet sixteen! shixa and jen came over and we took 70 bagillion hours to do our makeup. we partied it up with the gross dj. and jamjams guid moves, my moonwalk, and jen stepping on my feet kinda owned the dancefloor i must admit. it was totally like 8th grade all over again and it was pretty damn fun. 

today was jamjam's birthday. lodi buffet was yummy. i love being fat. <3 i don't feel good though. my eyes really hurt and i don't know why. and it sucks. heres to another sucky week of school. gooodbye.

i haven't written anything in awhile. whatup, livejournal.

florida was goood. me and mirna got black, caught some lizards, and ate alot. oh and i bought my new phone. after begging for the entire vacation. i've never been so happy to spend $400. and let me just tell you, florida has some of the sweetest shopping centers. they have an outdoor hollister! yes, outdooooooor. insane, i know. all in all it was funnnn. well-needed vacation right there. it went supa fast.

now i'm back in cold joisy. i missed everyone lots. we did like absolutely nothing in school, less work for me. next week i have stupid hspa, greeeeeat. whatever, i'm gonna soak up this weekend as much as i can if that's possible.

yesterday i went to radioshack with josh, jen, and jamjam. we tried to go to the mall, and even ran after the bus, but the stupid dick bus driver drove away. what a douchebag. we sucked it up and walked. we got yummy pizza, me and jen (aka the band-aid bandits) did a bad deed that should not be spoken of before the manager of harmon comes and eats us, and went to gamestop. and then caught the bus to my house because we're lazy!

we watched fight club at my houseeee. lead salad! lead pie! lead samich! blt? rofl oh man. i had a good friday, cept mirna and pema were missing.</3

i wub life.
that sounds cheesey.
but i really do.
http://aaanorexorcist.livejournal.com/2537.html

i'm going to florida tomorrow.
it shall be fun.




bye heights, i'll miss everyone.
http://aaanorexorcist.livejournal.com/2074.html

so basically, this weekend was pretty alrighttttt. i had stomach virus friday so i missed school. that made me sad. that's kinda not sarcasm. throwing up is never fun. except josh brought me soup and chocolate and stuff and i was happy. and i saw snakes on a plane! goood movie. mallinggg on saturday with jen, pema, mirna and jamjam was fun. especially running throughout the whole mall to try and get to the right place at the right time. of course me jen and mirna are speds and run outside the mall and back inside to get to our destination. what coolkids we are. cool and today was probably the good end to my weekend. i woke up early and went snowboarding with mirna and jen. and the plakalovic family, of course. first of all the name of my snowboard was wingnut. yes, wingnut. could it get any better. so wingnut, ponyboy, and hannah basically owned the slopes. we have some skills let me tell you. after two times down the bunny slope we were on the big hill, best believe. and me and mirna snuck onto the tubing line, while jen got left behind because she took too long to pick out a pretty colored tube. silly jen. so yeah, that was fun :] and i just watched a really good movie. i almost shed a tear, srsly. my ass is sore, for show. increase the peace.

since i'm not sleeping yet, i'm gonna write something. i've been really tired lately; it's annoying. exams are over, i did average. nothing special, but i didn't expect anything great considering i didn't study longer than 10 minutes for anything. this week went uber slow but whatever. tomorrow's friday and saturday is pema's birthday. happy early birthday pema! :] i think mirna might come to florida wif me. so rob can't sleep in his undies. rofl. i can't wait to get a tan and look guid. even though i already look guid i'm gonna stop talking but i'll leave with these lyrics since this song is amazing: With eyes so dialated, I've become your pupil. You've taught me everything, without a poison apple.

yesterday at bowling, me and pema almost mastered the curve. well not mastered, but we learned it. finallllly. today was really really fucking cold. well not that cold but colder than it's been lately.  it's sorta a good thing i guess; i don't wanna die of global warming. 
yay for rambling on about nothing. i'm gonna shutup now perche la mia laptop morto in 5 4 3 2 1 poof.

meredith's party was the shit. all four of us basically owned and everyone thought we were drunk. i love not caring what people think. :]]]
i miss josh a lot.

i'm done
